tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE UserInteractions (
    interaction_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    interaction_data JSONB,
    timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ
)

CREATE TABLE ChangesAudit (
    audit_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    change_type VARCHAR(50),
    change_data JSONB,
    timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ
)

CREATE TABLE SecurityMonitoring (
    notification_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    notification_type VARCHAR(50),
    notification_data JSONB,
    timestamp TIMESTAMPTZ
)

CREATE TABLE change_audit_log (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    table_name VARCHAR(255),
    action VARCHAR(255),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
